headline: 5 Things To Consider After Lumen's Mass Markets Fiber Asset Sale To AT&T
summary: Lumen's $5.75B fiber sale to AT&T reduces debt, boosts focus on AI and cloud services. Strong partnerships and growth potential earn it a 'Buy' rating.
